text: Billdal is a bimunicipal locality situated in Kungsbacka Municipality, Halland County, and Gothenburg Municipality, Västra Götaland County, in Sweden. It had 10,289 inhabitants in 2010. It mainly consists of villas and terraced houses, grouped along a windling coastline with many islands. ==Notable natives== *Dark Tranquillity *In Flames ==See also== *Greater Gothenburg == References == Category:Populated places in Halland County Category:Populated places in Västra Götaland County Category:Populated places in Gothenburg Municipality Category:Populated places in Kungsbacka Municipality Category:Metropolitan Gothenburg
